org.apache.hadoop.hbase.metrics

接口 Counter

  • 所有超级接口:
    Metric
    所有已知实现类:

    @InterfaceAudience.LimitedPrivate(value="Coprocesssor")
 @InterfaceStability.Evolving
public interface Counter
extends Metric
    A mutable number optimized for high concurrency counting.
